		}

		effect = {
			spawn_army = {
				name = event_troop_default_name
				levies = 600
				location = province:1811
				origin = province:1811
			}
		}
	}
	863.1.1 = {
		effect = {
			set_relation_rival = { reason = rival_historical target = character:yemeni0030 } #Historically actually this guy's son, Yahya Tuyyibid (the emir used the Tuyyibid to try to stop the ibn Musa power), but the son isn't in power yet, so we make it just the current Tuyyibid.
		}
	}
	867.1.1 = {
		add_unpressed_claim = title:c_calatayud
		add_unpressed_claim = title:c_zaragoza
		add_unpressed_claim = title:c_albarracin
		add_unpressed_claim = title:c_fraga

			add_gold = 150
			set_relation_rival = { reason = rival_historical target = character:levantine0008 }
		}
	}

		death = {
			death_reason = death_accident
		}
	}

					has_dlc_feature = roads_to_power
